  <body dur="03:05.660">
    <div begin="00:54.570" end="03:05.660">
      <p begin="00:54.570" end="01:01.520" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:54.570" end="00:55.460">浮</span><span begin="00:55.460" end="00:56.270">云</span><span begin="00:56.360" end="00:57.190">栖</span><span begin="00:57.250" end="00:57.760">山</span><span begin="00:58.230" end="00:58.630">意</span><span begin="00:58.720" end="01:00.850">更</span><span begin="01:00.950" end="01:01.520">深</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">浮雲棲山意更深</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Floating clouds rest on the mountain deepening the mood</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">浮雲 山に留まりて趣深く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">뜬구름 머무는 산에 정취는 더욱 깊어지고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les nuages flottants s'attardent sur la montagne et le sens s'approfondit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las nubes flotantes descansan en la montaña y el significado se profundiza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schwebende Wolken verweilen am Berg die Stimmung vertieft sich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As nuvens flutuantes repousam na montanha e o significado se aprofunda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Плывущие облака укрывают горы тая в себе глубокий смысл</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le nuvole fluttuanti riposano sulle montagne l'atmosfera si fa più profonda</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">veu yuin tshi se i ken sen</span></p>
      <p begin="01:01.910" end="01:08.830" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="01:01.910" end="01:02.380">漫</span><span begin="01:02.430" end="01:04.230">步</span><span begin="01:04.920" end="01:05.520">遥</span><span begin="01:05.590" end="01:06.550">见</span><span begin="01:06.550" end="01:07.450">有</span><span begin="01:07.510" end="01:08.410">鹤</span><span begin="01:08.460" end="01:08.830">引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">漫步遙見有鶴引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Strolling I see a crane leading the way from afar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">漫ろ歩けば遥か鶴の導き</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">거닐다 아득히 학이 이끄는 것을 보네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En flânant je vois au loin une grue qui me guide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Paseando veo a lo lejos una grulla que me guía</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Beim Wandern sehe ich aus der Ferne einen Kranich der mich führt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Caminhando sem pressa vejo de longe um grou a guiar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Прогуливаясь вдали вижу журавля указывающего путь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Passeggiando vedo da lontano una gru che mi fa da guida</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">moe bou yeu ki yeu hoh yin</span></p>
      <p begin="01:09.250" end="01:15.510" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="01:09.250" end="01:09.660">似</span><span begin="01:09.740" end="01:11.100">仙</span><span begin="01:11.130" end="01:11.610">人</span> <span begin="01:12.970" end="01:13.860">点</span><span begin="01:13.970" end="01:14.750">丹</span><span begin="01:14.820" end="01:15.510">青</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">似仙人 點丹青</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like an immortal painting</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">仙人の如く丹青を点ず</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마치 신선인 양 단청(그림)을 그리니</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Telle une immortelle apposant ses couleurs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como un inmortal pintando con tinta y acuarela</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie ein Unsterblicher der mit Tusche malt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como um imortal pincelando a pintura tradicional</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно небожитель взмахнувший кистью</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come un immortale che dipinge un quadro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">zy sie zen tie te tshin</span></p>
      <p begin="01:16.660" end="01:28.410" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="01:16.660" end="01:17.660">分</span><span begin="01:17.660" end="01:19.070">明</span><span begin="01:19.490" end="01:19.920">远</span><span begin="01:19.970" end="01:20.370">黛</span><span begin="01:20.490" end="01:21.380">两</span><span begin="01:21.380" end="01:22.110">弯</span><span begin="01:22.230" end="01:23.460">怎</span><span begin="01:23.530" end="01:23.740">失</span><span begin="01:24.050" end="01:26.010">声</span><span begin="01:26.010" end="01:28.410">音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">分明遠黛兩彎怎失聲音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Clearly two curves of distant dark mountains how did they lose their sound</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">鮮明なる遠き山波何故音を失う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">분명 아득한 먼 산봉우리건만 어찌 소리를 잃었는가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces deux courbes de montagnes lointaines si nettes comment ont-elles perdu leur voix</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Claramente son dos curvas de montañas oscuras cómo es que perdieron la voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Deutlich zwei Kurven ferner Berge warum verliert sich die Stimme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Claramente duas curvas de montanhas distantes como perderam a voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ясно вижу изгибы далёких гор но почему же стихли все звуки</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Chiaramente due curve di montagne lontane come sopracciglia come hanno perso la voce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">fen min yoe de lian ue tsen seh sen yin</span></p>
      <p begin="02:32.410" end="02:34.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="02:32.410" end="02:32.740">更</span><span begin="02:32.820" end="02:33.340">深</span><span begin="02:33.340" end="02:34.150">那</span><span begin="02:34.220" end="02:34.660">见</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">更深那見</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Seeing late at night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">夜更けに見ゆるは</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">밤이 깊어 그곳을 보니</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Au cœur de la nuit où l'ai-je vue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En la profundidad de la noche qué veo allí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In tiefer Nacht wo ist zu sehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Na calada da noite onde se vê</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кого же я вижу в глубокой ночи</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel cuore della notte chi appare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ken sen na ki</span></p>
      <p begin="02:35.100" end="02:40.150" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="02:35.100" end="02:35.960">是</span><span begin="02:36.040" end="02:37.400">谁</span><span begin="02:37.940" end="02:38.380">懒</span><span begin="02:38.430" end="02:38.870">倚</span><span begin="02:38.870" end="02:39.230">又</span><span begin="02:39.300" end="02:39.720">散</span><span begin="02:39.810" end="02:40.150">鬓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">是誰懶倚又散鬢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Who is it lazily leaning with loose hair</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">誰ぞ気怠く寄りかかり鬢を解く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">흩어진 머리로 나른하게 기대어 있는 이는 누구인가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Qui est celle qui s'appuie paresseusement les cheveux dénoués</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quién se apoya perezosamente con el cabello suelto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wer lehnt dort träge mit gelöstem Haar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quem se apoia preguiçosamente com os cabelos soltos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кто это лениво прислонился с распущенными волосами</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Chi è colei che si appoggia pigramente con i capelli sciolti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">zy zei le i yeu se pin</span></p>
      <p begin="02:40.650" end="02:47.680" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="02:40.650" end="02:41.170">拂</span><span begin="02:41.170" end="02:41.570">衣</span><span begin="02:41.660" end="02:42.040">对</span><span begin="02:42.070" end="02:43.290">坐</span><span begin="02:43.410" end="02:43.530">无</span><span begin="02:43.530" end="02:43.890">意</span><span begin="02:44.340" end="02:44.530">一</span><span begin="02:44.570" end="02:46.160">树</span><span begin="02:46.210" end="02:47.680">雨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">拂衣對坐無意一樹雨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Brushing clothes and sitting opposite paying no mind to a tree of rain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">衣払い対座し一樹の雨も介さず</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">옷깃 떨치고 마주 앉아 나무에 내리는 비는 아랑곳 않네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Lissant mes vêtements je m'assois face à elle ignorant la pluie sur l'arbre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sacudo mi ropa y me siento frente a ti ignorando la lluvia sobre el árbol</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Gewand abstreifend gegenübersitzend dem Regen im Baum keine Beachtung schenkend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sacudindo as vestes sentando frente a frente sem ligar para a chuva na árvore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Оправив одежды мы сидим друг напротив друга не замечая шума дождя в листве</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Scuoto le vesti e mi siedo di fronte a te ignorando la pioggia sull'albero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">feh i teu zou vu i yih zyu yu</span></p>
      <p begin="02:48.160" end="02:54.250" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="02:48.160" end="02:48.520">漫</span><span begin="02:48.580" end="02:48.980">聊</span><span begin="02:49.030" end="02:49.420">来</span><span begin="02:49.470" end="02:50.150">兴</span><span begin="02:50.910" end="02:51.760">知</span><span begin="02:51.830" end="02:52.750">音</span><span begin="02:52.750" end="02:54.020">难</span><span begin="02:54.100" end="02:54.250">觅</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">漫聊來興知音難覓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Casually chatting with rising interest a soulmate is hard to find</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">語らいに興乗るも知音は得難し</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">흥에 겨워 이야기 나누나 지기(知己)를 찾기란 어렵구나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Discutant au gré de l'inspiration une véritable âme sœur est si rare à trouver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Charlando con entusiasmo sabiendo que un alma gemela es difícil de encontrar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Im Plaudern erwacht die Freude ein Seelenverwandter ist schwer zu finden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Conversando à vontade conforme a inspiração é difícil encontrar uma alma gêmea</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В лёгкой беседе рождается вдохновение ведь так редко встретишь родственную душу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Chiacchierando spensieratamente un vero confidente è difficile da trovare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">moe lieu le shin tsy yin ne mih</span></p>
      <p begin="02:54.560" end="03:05.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="02:54.560" end="02:55.050">哪</span><span begin="02:55.050" end="02:55.410">还</span><span begin="02:55.470" end="02:55.900">记</span><span begin="02:55.970" end="02:56.130">得</span><span begin="02:56.350" end="02:56.830">再</span><span begin="02:56.860" end="02:58.260">问</span><span begin="02:58.300" end="02:58.810">是</span><span begin="02:59.250" end="03:00.070">梦</span><span begin="03:00.140" end="03:00.920">或</span><span begin="03:00.970" end="03:01.420">是</span><span begin="03:01.880" end="03:03.090">醒</span><span begin="03:03.090" end="03:05.660">也</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪還記得再問是夢或是醒也</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Who even remembers to ask again whether this is a dream or reality</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">夢か現か再び問うことすら忘れて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이것이 꿈인지 생시인지 묻는 것조차 잊어버렸네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Qui se souvient encore de demander si c'est un rêve ou la réalité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cómo podría acordarme de preguntar de nuevo si es un sueño o si estoy despierta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wer denkt noch daran zu fragen ob es Traum oder Erwachen ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como ainda lembrar de perguntar de novo se é sonho ou vigília</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И кто теперь вспомнит спросить сон это или явь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Chi si ricorda più di chiedere se questo sia un sogno o la realtà</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">na we ki teh tse men zy mon hoh zy sin ya</span></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
